: Rage continued to sniff at the stasis locked body of Reptilica before 
something else caught her attention, something that had turned its attention 
on HER.
However, with her prey so close like this, it would be very stupid to ignore 
this opportunity now.
She opened her massive mouth, saliva streaming from the spaces between her 
teeth, onto to have a roar of pain to emerge instead of the head of her prey 
to enter it.
Something had hit her in the neck!
Rage snapped her head towards the direction where the hit had come from, 
where the stun charge from DevilDuers causing her neck to slow become numb.
The back of her jaw was also becoming numb, but she barely noticed as her 
keen sight zeroed in on one particular being aiming something at her.
That HAD to be the one that had hit her.
She shook her head and neck to try and dispel the feeling that was creeping 
up the back of her skull, her mouth opening to reveal her teeth and a loud 
bellow of anger screaming towards the bot whom had shot her.
With packed muscles Rage was thundering across the distance between her and 
the intended victim(DD), her huge shadow descending upon the Alliance bot 
with a mouth of razor sharp teeth in lead of the bulk of her body.
Noone spoiled her meal and got away with it.!:
